wikipedia_page.main: Freddy Daniel Moncur (born 8 September 1996) is an English professional footballer who plays for Grays Athletic as a midfielder.

response: Moncur is the son of former Tottenham Hotspur, Swindon Town and West Ham midfielder John Moncur, and the older brother of former Leyton Orient midfielder Freddy Moncur. He carries a tattoo dedicated to his former West Ham teammate Dylan Tombides, who died in April 2014 from testicular cancer.
